    "text": "Clarifying Remanufacturing to Protect Patient Safety Act of 2022\n\nThis bill specifies that entities that remanufacture medical devices in a manner that could change the performance or safety specifications or the intended use of the device must register with the Food and Drug Administration as producers of medical devices and comply with related requirements."
